a scene at someone's business?

213
00:12:30,783 --> 00:12:31,551
Right?

214
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:33,801
It just looked like I was
causing a scene to you, right?

215
00:12:34,387 --> 00:12:36,341
I used to do reports
from Prosecutor's Office...

216
00:12:36,426 --> 00:12:37,849
...police stations and congress.

217
00:12:37,934 --> 00:12:40,159
