219
00:12:44,052 --> 00:12:45,355
A waste of talent.

220
00:12:48,834 --> 00:12:50,784
Is that why you're
trying to get reinstated?

221
00:12:52,567 --> 00:12:53,321
Did you see it?

222
00:12:53,406 --> 00:12:54,500
Of course I did.

223
00:12:54,593 --> 00:12:57,129
You put in on top of your desk,
so I'd see it.

224
00:12:58,620 --> 00:13:00,001
Why aren't you answering me?

225
00:13:00,102 --> 00:13:01,547
Are you going to go back to work?

226
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,115
Yes.

227
00:13:07,061 --> 00:13:09,267
You said you saw yourself die
as a reporter in your dream.

228
00:13:09,355 --> 00:13:11,257
You said you can't be a reporter
anymore because you're scared.

229
00:13:11,562 --> 00:13:13,942
You said you were going to
work with me at this restaurant.

230
