252
00:13:55,154 --> 00:13:59,656
To me, you're not as
reliable or strong as him.

253
00:13:59,741 --> 00:14:01,236
I'm more worried about you.

254
00:14:01,321 --> 00:14:02,159
Much more...

255
00:14:05,225 --> 00:14:06,812
You're more precious to me than him.

256
00:14:12,501 --> 00:14:15,735
You're the only one
I have in this world also.

257
00:14:17,924 --> 00:14:19,625
So don't leave me alone.

258
00:14:22,228 --> 00:14:22,929
