618
00:34:38,862 --> 00:34:40,332
...patrolling around Myungwon University?

619
00:34:40,417 --> 00:34:43,856
Okay. Then let's eat
stir-fried blood sausage quickly...

620
00:34:43,941 --> 00:34:45,468
...and go patrol
around Myungwon University.

621
00:34:48,249 --> 00:34:49,500
I'll drive.

622
00:34:49,601 --> 00:34:50,734
So let's go on the patrol first.

623
00:34:51,095 --> 00:34:54,133
Maybe, you're right.

624
00:34:55,543 --> 00:34:57,026
Let's do it.

625
00:35:04,367 --> 00:35:07,001
Hey. Where are you
going at this hour?

626
00:35:07,100 --> 00:35:08,300
Mom. I might be late today.

627
00:35:08,367 --> 00:35:09,089
Don't wait up.

628
00:35:09,174 --> 00:35:11,968
Where are you going?
What is this?

629
00:35:12,033 --> 00:35:13,511
I'm going to save someone.

630
00:35:13,596 --> 00:35:15,001
Someone got hurt in my dream.

631
00:35:18,834 --> 00:35:22,001
Mom. Promise me one thing.

632
00:35:23,667 --> 00:35:26,512
If I change my dream this time...

633
00:35:27,428 --> 00:35:29,386
...and save that person...

634
00:35:30,595 --> 00:35:32,947
