637
00:36:16,538 --> 00:36:18,476
Chohee. Chohee.

638
00:36:19,033 --> 00:36:20,011
I'm so glad.

639
00:36:32,767 --> 00:36:33,958
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

640
00:36:34,767 --> 00:36:37,582
You might not believe it,
but I just stopped a big accident.

641
00:36:37,667 --> 00:36:40,201
What are you talking about right now?

642
00:36:40,300 --> 00:36:41,717
This took so long to prepare.

643
00:36:41,802 --> 00:36:43,502
Do you know what I went
through to prepare this?

644
00:36:43,601 --> 00:36:45,102
What are you doing?

645
00:36:50,467 --> 00:36:51,477
Hey. Stop there!

646
00:37:10,714 --> 00:37:12,706
Hey. Where did she go?

647
00:37:15,897 --> 00:37:17,492
