650
00:38:00,378 --> 00:38:03,835
In my dream, a female student got burned
because of the Candle Light Event.

651
00:38:03,928 --> 00:38:06,533
So I put the fire out with
the fire extinguisher.

652
00:38:06,766 --> 00:38:08,836
