...it was that woman from
the cafe that we go to everyday.

654
00:38:11,701 --> 00:38:12,792
Isn't that amazing?

655
00:38:14,749 --> 00:38:16,395
Did you come because
you dreamt about me too?

656
00:38:16,934 --> 00:38:21,133
Recently Wootak said that you
dream about me often these days.

657
00:38:21,868 --> 00:38:22,948
I wonder why?

658
00:38:23,033 --> 00:38:25,934
Is because opposites attract?
Are you nervous for no reason?

659
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:26,901
Is it fate?

660
00:38:31,558 --> 00:38:32,873
I'm sorry about back then.

661
00:38:32,968 --> 00:38:33,968
And thank you.

662
00:38:34,084 --> 00:38:35,001
Back then?

663
00:38:35,334 --> 00:38:36,202
When are you talking about?

664
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:38,716
When you took my side
at your restaurant...

665
00:38:39,167 --> 00:38:40,200
Back then...

666
00:38:40,300 --> 00:38:41,867
I didn't take your side.

667
00:38:41,982 --> 00:38:43,435
I just told the truth.

668
00:38:45,092 --> 00:38:46,023
Then I take it back.

669
00:38:47,200 --> 00:38:48,984
By the way, did you make up your mind?

670
00:38:49,339 --> 00:38:52,901
Would you indict that person who aided
and abetted that drunk driver or not?

671
00:38:55,167 --> 00:38:56,013
I'd indict him.

672
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:58,783
Why?
It's not like he caused the accident.

673
00:38:58,868 --> 00:39:00,320
You're going to indict him
for only giving him the keys?

