to beat up someone, weren't you?

695
00:40:12,668 --> 00:40:13,616
No. We weren't.

696
00:40:13,701 --> 00:40:19,402
You can't run around like hyenas looking
for rotten meat and beat up people.

697
00:40:19,501 --> 00:40:20,422
Do you understand?

698
00:40:20,507 --> 00:40:23,036
Follow me. Follow me.

699
00:40:23,121 --> 00:40:24,830
Why are you doing that?
Follow me.

700
00:40:24,915 --> 00:40:26,703
Follow me.

701
