704
00:40:36,699 --> 00:40:40,035
I'm not, but it feels like its burning.

705
00:40:40,267 --> 00:40:41,400
I wonder what's wrong with me.

706
00:40:46,801 --> 00:40:47,801
Hello.

707
00:40:53,367 --> 00:40:54,634
Daehee.

708
00:40:57,157 --> 00:41:00,157
What happened?

709
00:41:03,042 --> 00:41:03,843
Daehee.

710
00:41:05,578 --> 00:41:07,127
Can you hear me?

711
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:13,834
He's not opening his eyes.

712
00:41:14,734 --> 00:41:18,155
Daehee. This is not true, right?

713
00:41:19,067 --> 00:41:20,951
What happened?

714
00:41:24,252 --> 00:41:27,081
Why is his body so cold?

715
00:41:27,868 --> 00:41:31,345
