716
00:41:33,100 --> 00:41:36,567
I took his shift and now
I have to observe an autopsy...

717
00:41:36,667 --> 00:41:39,274
The curse of Han River District
Prosecutors' Office strikes again.

718
00:41:39,359 --> 00:41:41,235
