722
00:41:48,447 --> 00:41:49,547
I know, right?

723
00:41:51,801 --> 00:41:52,868
Just a moment.

724
00:41:55,300 --> 00:41:58,849
He's not bleeding much for
the severity of the accident.

725
00:41:59,192 --> 00:42:01,432
-Should we perform the autopsy?
-No.

726
00:42:02,557 --> 00:42:04,102
I don't want the autopsy.

727
00:42:04,767 --> 00:42:05,961
But in order to find
the truth of his death.

728
00:42:06,046 --> 00:42:07,767
No. You can't do that.

729
00:42:08,003 --> 00:42:09,470
I killed him.

730
00:42:09,555 --> 00:42:13,868
He could've taken the bus but I drove him.

731
00:42:13,953 --> 00:42:15,333
I'm the one who killed him.

732
00:42:16,397 --> 00:42:19,370
