let's skip the autopsy.

733
00:42:32,953 --> 00:42:34,353
I'm home.

734
00:42:37,465 --> 00:42:38,320
Wow.

735
00:42:38,405 --> 00:42:40,195
Why did you buy so many crabs?

736
00:42:47,653 --> 00:42:50,669
