737
00:42:50,754 --> 00:42:52,603
The student who got hurt in my dream.

738
00:42:54,483 --> 00:42:56,512
So as you promised...

739
00:42:56,597 --> 00:42:58,158
I never promised.

740
00:42:58,300 --> 00:42:59,867
You're the one who said
I promised on your own.

741
00:43:05,012 --> 00:43:05,878
Mom.

742
00:43:06,447 --> 00:43:08,868
You know that I like writing in my diary.

743
00:43:09,172 --> 00:43:11,667
I wrote in my journal every day
in my teens...

744
00:43:11,767 --> 00:43:14,127
...even if I couldn't
sleep for more than an hour.

745
00:43:15,249 --> 00:43:18,186
