criticizing my superiors at work.

746
00:43:20,200 --> 00:43:22,647
But I finish writing in
it after I write six lines.

747
00:43:23,637 --> 00:43:25,096
It's similar to yesterday.

748
00:43:26,294 --> 00:43:27,741
I can even write ahead of time.

749
00:43:27,883 --> 00:43:29,379
It will be similar tomorrow.

750
00:43:31,730 --> 00:43:34,416
I saw that the whole year's worth...

751
00:43:34,501 --> 00:43:36,335
...wasn't even as long as
one day worth from before.

752
00:43:36,708 --> 00:43:38,309
