753
00:43:43,602 --> 00:43:44,436
Mom.

754
00:43:45,133 --> 00:43:49,536
I just want today to be a little more
wonderful than the day before.

755
00:43:50,063 --> 00:43:52,535
I don't want to waste by doing
nothing just because I'm scared.

756
00:43:52,620 --> 00:43:55,082
So you're going to go back to work?

757
00:43:55,391 --> 00:43:57,192
Even though you dreamed that you saw
yourself die as a reporter in your dream?

758
00:43:58,410 --> 00:44:00,015
I'm not going to die.

759
00:44:00,100 --> 00:44:01,672
I can just change my dream.

760
00:44:02,746 --> 00:44:05,735
I can change the dream after
I met Jaechan and Wootak.

761
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:07,224
I changed it today too.

762
00:44:07,501 --> 00:44:08,712
I understood while
I was changing the future.

763
00:44:09,722 --> 00:44:13,268
